Show HN: I made a builder that lets you create a sales page for Gumroad products
text:
Hey everyone, Would love to hear your feedback

I just released the beta for a no-code builder specifically for people selling on Gumroad.

Seeing lots of artsy and non-technical folks selling through Gumroad, their only real option when advertising is to create a sales page throuh something like Square or Wix.

Like all non-niche things, this becomes hard when you actually want to link up your payment and email subscribers directly to your page. (Not to even mention affiliate sellers).

Wrapping gum is my response to this

So if you're a seller on Gumroad, would love to hear some feedback from you on whether or not you would find this usefull or not

Brutal feedback is always encouraged :)

Thank you
